src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n淘寶果啲msdn key隨時畀m$封（或重裝後隨時失效）<br />\nOEM key就穩陣好多（綁底版同支援重裝）<br />\n<br />\n至於有人問點解唔索性用破解<br />\n好明顯係基於安全問題（怕有毒同後門）<br />\n<br />\np.s. win 8.1 零售版升上去10的到此一遊"},{"pid":"9fd3b0721f62c2a7648e5abda269b687f35fc22d","tid":105570,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T00:47:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>比錢買翻版<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n點都好過有啲人一個仙都唔想畀人賺仲要屌人垃圾但係又keep住用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7fbeec93126bd33cf1def77226bc458e809da702","tid":105570,"uid":28563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T01:35:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>比錢買翻版<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n點都好過有啲人一個仙都唔想畀人賺仲要屌人垃圾但係又keep住用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有幾好？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n晒果幾十蚊買條key以為自己用正版，到頭黎同用windows loader果班人冇分別<br />\n自我安慰<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1780e5d1a9ee63cb745d87c751f7731eca164500","tid":105570,"uid":36533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T01:39:52.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c26663d3206c8e8794c1c0b7398c12f0809a1c54","tid":105570,"uid":28563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T01:44:12.000Z","msg":"你呢個counter argument簡直廢到暈，你都係power_off把啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n比錢買oem key，經偉大既ms開聲之後，變晒做老翻，依家同用crack/買老翻碟冇分別，一樣做到完美更新，ms一樣查唔到。<br />\n<br />\n可能有人會跳出黎話windows loader/其他crack有毒，我想講我部windows vm只係裝game，同所有重要file隔離，唔似你地咁乜狗屎垃圾都擺係windows，一中毒不得了。<br />\n<br />\n比錢買老翻碟既人自我感覺良好過上網down破解既人，真係好笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9bc2bc2d74443cb009dc37ad6e1e850e184bc732","tid":105570,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T02:20:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你呢個counter argument簡直廢到暈，你都係power_off把啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n比錢買oem key，經偉大既ms開聲之後，變晒做老翻，依家同用crack/買老翻碟冇分別，一樣做到完美更新，ms一樣查唔到。<br />\n<br />\n可能有人會跳出黎話windows loader/其他crack有毒，我想講我部windows vm只係裝game，同所有重要file隔離，唔似你地咁乜狗屎垃圾都擺係windows，一中毒不得了。<br />\n<br />\n比錢買老翻碟既人自我感覺良好過上網down破解既人，真係好笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n用老翻用到你咁自豪，果然名不虛傳呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n影衰哂其他linux user<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab88db8eb105d8ce3acfc2a87b7e414efa96dfc6","tid":105570,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T02:23:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>可能有人會跳出黎話windows loader/其他crack有毒，我想講我部windows vm只係裝game，同所有重要file隔離，唔似你地咁乜狗屎垃圾都擺係windows，一中毒不得了。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n留意返，係佢地，唔包括我。<br />\n<br />\n我有裝防毒(bitdefender)，部腦裡面全部嘢用正版，一直以來相安無事。"},{"pid":"898fc320047236f41c45b35f2469ecf62e89f004","tid":105570,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T02:29:26.000Z","msg":"對於一般用家嚟講，入key啟用軟件遠比破解版安全，佢地並唔係你，唔會做到咁極端。"},{"pid":"74fbf601495592cbeee9ad2f2e785607a2b98a64","tid":105570,"uid":34010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T02:33:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>你呢個counter argument簡直廢到暈，你都係power_off把啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n比錢買oem key，經偉大既ms開聲之後，變晒做老翻，依家同用crack/買老翻碟冇分別，一樣做到完美更新，ms一樣查唔到。<br />\n<br />\n可能有人會跳出黎話windows loader/其他c